songs.lyrics:
[Intro]
I don't wanna talk right now (Right Now)
Tori  on the beat
I  been busy getting to the guap right now (Right now)
Thanks Ugly God, thanks Ugly God
Thanks Ugly God, thanks Ugly God

[Chorus]
I  don’t wanna talk right now (Right now)
I  been busy getting to the guap right now (Right now)
I pull up on my opps right now
'Cause  I got 30 shots up in this Glock right now (Right now)
Louis for the bag (Bag), I don't like to brag (Brag)
All I ever wanted was to throw a lot of cash (Cash)
So I’m really busy gettin' to the guap right now (Right now)
I  don't got the time to take a loss right now (Right now)

[Verse]
Bring her to the room then you know it's lights out
I see you talkin' shit but I bet I fuck yo' bitch (Bitch)
She think I'm a plumber cause I lay that pipe down
I throw my money up, think it's coming right down
Thanks Ugly God, thanks Ugly God
Right down
I say what I want, fuck how I might sound
And I do what I please so you need to pipe down
Keep my name out your mouth before I make you bite down
(Bite down)
Right now
I got hella hoes, white, dark and light brown
I know I made you mad when I see that slight frown
I seen a couple things that I need to write down
When I hit her from the back it’s gon’ make a nice sound
You look like a queen when you in a night gown
When my money in my hands it adds a whole hunnid' pounds
And this choppa in my hand hold a whole hunnid’ round (Round)

[Chorus]
I don't wanna talk right now (Right now)
I been busy getting to the guap right now (Right now)
I pull up on my opps right now
'Cause I got 30 shots up in this Glock right now (Right now)
Louis for the bag (Bag), I don't like to brag (Brag)
All I ever wanted was to throw a lot of cash (Cash)
So I’m really busy gettin' to the guap right now (Right now)
I don't got the time to take a loss right now (Right now)

[Outro]
Thanks Ugly God, thanks Ugly God
Thanks Ugly God, thanks Ugly God
songs.title: Right Now
